parameters:
\nc<>It looked like my hand was touching Senpai's butt... Was it
just my misunderstanding?

\nc<>Ah, no. It's not a misunderstanding... Thanks to you, I was
saved.

\nc<>Is that so? I'm glad... well, not really. I went through
such an experience.

\nc<>But it's okay, Senpai! I got a good look at that person's
face!
\nc<>If we report it, they should be caught right away.

\ncExcuse me. I heard that you were a victim of molestation.
Are you the victim?

\ncI will quickly conduct an interview so that we can respond
immediately. What was the appearance of the molester like?

\nc<>I saw it! They were wearing a black jacket and a knitted
hat.

\ncI confirmed that they were wearing a black jacket and a
knitted hat... What happened inside the subway?
\nc<>I was touched on my butt and... um, my crotch.
\nc<Female Police Officer>What do you mean by crotch? Please explain it accurately.
\nc<Female Police Officer>I see. Did you feel it when your clit was touched?

\nc<>Hey, what have you been asking me all this time! There's no
way a woman would feel pleasure from being molested!

\ncExcuse me. However, recently there have been cases where
they pretend to agree and then threaten to report...

\ncWe have been instructed to confirm it according to the
guidelines. Thank you for your cooperation.
\nc<>If that's the case, then there's no helping it...

\nc<>But it's okay. Senpai is not a pervert who would feel
pleasure from being molested.

\ncI see. In that case, could you show me what's inside your
skirt?
\nc<Female Police Officer>Why are you so surprised?

\nc<>T-That's... umm... I don't think I can show it to you
directly...

\ncIt's okay, I just need to confirm if you felt anything. It
will only take a moment.

\nc<>Well, it's fine, Senpai. We're both women after all. No one
will see us here.

\nc...I'm sorry, but it seems difficult to file a groping
complaint.

\ncInstead of that, it's better to say that you were groped in
that state... Ahem, I'm sorry. My true feelings slipped out.

\ncI will pretend I didn't see what happened this time... Let's
keep the playing with fire to a minimum.

\nc<>Y-You don't need to worry, Senpai! Everyone has their own
preferences.

\nc<>No! This is because of the villain, my body has become
strange...!
\nc<>Ah, y-yes! It's because of the villain, right? I understand!

\nc<>(...Let's try not to meet with the female police officer
here for a while.)
\nc<>I obtained the proof ticket Reina A-2.
\nc<>The number of bad listeners has increased by 2000.
